  "content": [
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Something I’ve noticed while working on teams of all sizes is that it’s often hard for people to communicate with one another efficiently ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "and",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "effectively.",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Many times, for example, many people talk at the same time, which complicates things for a variety of reasons:",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Because people are so focused on getting ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "their",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "point across (as opposed to listening), they rarely focus on the other people doing the talking.",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "And because those people are never heard, conflicts arise because no one actually hears what’s been said.",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "A simple, low-cost solution: buy a ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "beach ball",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ", pass it around. The person with the ball gets to talk. Everyone else just listens.",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "This gives the ball-holder ample time to communicate their point. While everyone else gets to listen ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "intently",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ", and think concretely about what they are going to say in response (instead of merely spitting it out).",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Sure, it’s juvenile. But it may be the best way to train your team (and yourself) to communicate like an adult.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
